[Scene01]

Arnold's bombs had worked just as prescribed and fires
began to spread throughout the base as the explosives detonated. 
Attaching his emergency teleportation device to Teeka, Bob sent the
scout to safety and quickly hurried to the base's rear exit.

[Scene02]

But even as the warning lights bathed his surroundings in a deep red
and the sounds of the alarms threatened to deafen him, Bob discovered
that the enemy forces were not willing to let him escape without
putting up a fight. But he who fights and runs away...

[END]
